{"tid":1769670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃色經濟圈」唔怕你扮黃 最怕扮唔似","createTime":"2019-12-05T04:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T10:43:49.000Z","uid":285880,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd88f6b941d3893424fcf387dc1d7f1b21e5e0f","tid":1769670,"uid":285880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"對於黃色經濟圈，我認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首要任務應該係消滅藍店</span></span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再次就係壯大黃店</span></span>。<br />\n好明顯，我地仲做緊首要任務，所以呢個時候，真係<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔怕藍扮黃</span></span>。要監察既，應該係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">扮得似唔似</span></span>。<br />\n例如學生係咪有優惠或免費，有無貼文宣，有無罷工，有無發夢派野等等。<br />\n道理就似一個藍絲扮黃，如果佢扮到選舉都投黃，咁其實係無問題，仲好符合我地目標。<br />\n<br />\n換句話講，其實我地做緊既野，同中共收編各行各業，邏輯同做法上係一樣。重要既係我地既理念比中共正義。<br />\n<br />\n所以，唔洗怕人扮黃，佢肯扮就更加要佢扮得足，扮得似。當<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">消滅完藍，我地再將淺黃變深黃，深黃變金</span></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n前提係，團結，齊心，不分化，不割席，不篤灰。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"220752f0c423b64bc262454b109865270f7c8586","tid":1769670,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"英國美國加拿大都攻擊緊中國<br />\n但啲tweets無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Rt + like + reply</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=65a4ec73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task2</spa